    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Dialog: Select Elements</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Select Elements</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Table">If there is ambiguity as to which <text styleclass="Element">Element(s)</text> to select to continue or complete a command, the <text styleclass="Interface">Select Elements dialog-box</text><text style="font-weight:normal;">&#32;</text>opens <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">automatically</text>. </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Table">E.g.: <text styleclass="T_Menu">Add Pin-Joint</text> - and you click three <text styleclass="Element">Points</text>. You must select two <text styleclass="Element">Points</text> in the <text styleclass="Element">Select-Elements dialog-box</text>. </para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Select-Elements dialog-box</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Standard" rowcount="2" colcount="2" style="border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; cell-border-width:0px; border-style:none;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:201px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="Dialog-SelectElements-RefHelp.ipp" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"><caption><![CDATA[Select-Elements dialog-box]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="Body Text">To select the elements, do<text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><table styleclass="PopupTable2" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="width:100%;">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="6" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table"><image src="Ctrlb.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:6pt; vertical-align:sub;"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:6pt; vertical-align:sub;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold;">+</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:bold;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT">Click </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="color:#ff0000;">ALL</text><text styleclass="Body Text">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Element">elements</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> to continue or complete a command.</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Table">The <image src="OK-tiny-11-15.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image> becomes colorized only after you select element(s) that are consistent with the active command.</para>
                <list id="6" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;">Click</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:bold;">&#32;</text><image src="OK-tiny-11-15.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Body Text"> to close the </text><text styleclass="Interface">Select-Elements dialog-box</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Table">If the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-Manager" styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager</link> is also active:</para>
                <list id="6" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table">Continue to select the elements, as required. </li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Table">and / or</para>
                <list id="6" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table">Click <image src="OK-tiny-11-15.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image> in the <text styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager</text> to complete the command.</li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
